text.tspan: Assign Suits to major obstacles. Reveal Fate
- Sweep edge across all of Target
Rivals, Allies, and obsurment offer Cover
- Cover makes it harder to hit the Target
IF no obstacle THEN Line of Sight
Measure from center of your Space to Target
- Use a straight edge between dots
Most effects require line of sight to the target
IF Suit match THEN Target is the obstacle
